        <ArticleTitle>Discrimination of painting style and quality: pigeons use different strategies for different tasks.</ArticleTitle>
        <Pagination>
          <StartPage>797</StartPage>
          <EndPage>808</EndPage>
          <MedlinePgn>797-808</MedlinePgn>
